SubjectCanada-Korea - Agreement for Science, Technology and Innovation Cooperation
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Foreign Affairs to take the actions necessary to BRING INTO FORCE for Canada the AGREEMENT FOR SCIENCE, TECHNOLOGY AND INNOVATION COOPERATION between the Government of Canada and the Government of the REPUBLIC OF KOREA, done at Seoul on December 20, 2016.
